spec_data.Name: nodejs-encoding
spec_data.Description:
encoding is a simple wrapper around node-iconv and iconv-lite to convert
strings from one encoding to another. If node-iconv is not available for
some reason, iconv-lite will be used instead of it as a fallback.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 02:39:02 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Convert encodings, uses iconv by default and falls back to iconv-lite if needed
